00:29:51,069 --> 00:29:52,099
Kudengar Anda mencariku.

363
00:29:53,030 --> 00:29:56,740
Udara pagi ini sangat dingin.

364
00:29:57,000 --> 00:29:59,809
Seharusnya Anda berada di kamar. Kenapa Anda keluar?

365
00:30:09,250 --> 00:30:10,819
Jika dilihat dari kelembapan angin,

366
00:30:12,720 --> 00:30:15,059
